title: House maid ‘gang raped’ in Taxila - Pakistan - DAWN.COM
content:
TAXILA: A house maid was allegedly gang raped by four persons including a rickshaw driver in Jasian village in the limits of Attock Saddar police station on Wednesday, police sources said.

The victim reported to police that she was a house maid by profession and the rickshaw driver introduced her to Gull Khan to get her work in a house in Jasian village and took her to a house where he along with others gang raped her and fled.

Attock Saddar police have registered a case against the nominated accused after medical examination of the victim that confirmed the multiple rapes. Later, police arrested two suspects.

Published in Dawn, July 10th, 2025
